ZH: 我经常回家吃晚饭。
EN: I often go back home for dinner.

ZH: 他每周回公司开会。
EN: He goes back to the office for meetings every week.

ZH: 你什么时候回家？
EN: When are you going back home?

ZH: 她回家之后就去睡觉了。
EN: She goes to bed after going back home.

ZH: 我回去拿我的钱包。
EN: I am going back to get my wallet.

ZH: 我会尽快回你的消息。
EN: I will reply to your message as soon as possible.

ZH: 明天我回来取东西。
EN: I will come back tomorrow to pick up the items.

ZH: 请问这趟火车什么时候回到终点站？
EN: Excuse me, when will this train return to the final station?

ZH: 我们不久将回到中国。
EN: We will be returning to China soon.

ZH: 请记得回家看看爷爷奶奶。
EN: Please remember to go back home and visit your grandparents.

ZH: 困难的时候不要轻易回避，勇敢面对。
EN: Do not easily avoid difficulties, face them bravely.

ZH: 回顾过去，前进未来。
EN: Look back on the past, move forward to the future.

ZH: 遇到问题不要回避，要积极地解决。
EN: Do not avoid problems when you encounter them, actively solve them.

ZH: 回归自然，追求心灵平静。
EN: Returning to nature, seeking inner peace.

ZH: 我们决定回家休息一下。
EN: We decided to go back home and take a break.

ZH: 对不起，我之前的回答有误。
EN: I'm sorry, my previous reply was incorrect.

ZH: 他回想起小时候发生的有趣事情，不禁笑了起来。
EN: He remembered the funny things that happened when he was a child, and couldn't help but laugh.

ZH: 回转球场上的辉煌瞬间，那是一场不可磨灭的胜利。
EN: Reliving the glorious moments on the field, that was an indelible victory.

ZH: 为了更好地回应客户的需求，我们不断推出新产品。
EN: In order to better respond to the needs of customers, we continuously launch new products.

ZH: 回首历史，感受变迁，明天会更好。
EN: Looking back on history, feeling the changes, tomorrow will be better.
